# {{lb|en|archaic}} Given to [[misusing]]; also, full of abuses.
#* {{quote-book|passage=The '''abusive''' prerogatives of his see.|author=[[w:Henry Hallam|Hallam]]}}
# {{lb|en|obsolete}} Given to misusing. {{defdate|Attested only in the mid 17<sup>th</sup> century.}}<ref name=SOED/>
