# [[wrongly|Wrongly]] used; [[perverted]]; [[misapplied]]; [[unjust]]; illegal. {{defdate|First attested in the mid 16<sup>th</sup> century.}}<ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=10}}</ref>
